== Project Info ==

post-mode is a major mode for editing emails and newsgroup posts when using clients like Mutt and slrn. It is available from [https://github.com/Boruch-Baum/post-mode here].

== Configuration ==

Put post.el in your load-path and add the following snipplet to your .emacs file:

 (require 'post)

== Documentation ==

A French howto was available but seems to have gone missing.  Please update this page if you know where it is.

Otherwise, all documentation can be found on [https://github.com/Boruch-Baum/post-mode the Github project site].

